t]]\n[[Category:NBC original programming]]\n[[Category:Television series by Universal Television]]\n[[Category:Television series by Wolf Films]]\n[[Category:Television series created by Dick Wolf]]\n[[Category:Television shows featuring audio description]]\n[[Category:Television shows set in Chicago]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American police procedural drama television series}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=September 2017}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Chicago P.D.\n| image              = Title Card for Chicago P.D.jpg\n| image_alt          = \n| genre              = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Police procedural]]\n* [[Drama (genre)|Drama]]\n}}\n| creator            = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Dick Wolf]]\n* [[Matt Olmstead]]\n}}\n| developer          = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Derek Haas]]\n* [[Michael Brandt]]\n}}\n| starring           = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Jason Beghe]]\n* [[Jon Seda]]\n* [[Sophia Bush]]\n* [[Jesse Lee Soffer]]\n* [[Patrick John Flueger]]\n* [[Marina Squerciati]]\n* [[LaRoyce Hawkins]]\n* [[Archie Kao]]\n* [[Elias Koteas]]\n* [[Amy Morton]]\n* [[Brian Geraghty]]\n* [[Tracy Spiridakos]]\n* Lisseth Chavez\n}}\n| opentheme          = \n| endtheme           = \n| composer           = [[Atli \u00d6rvarsson]]\n| country            = United States\n| language           = English\n| num_seasons        = 7<!--Only increment as a new season premieres, per the documentation of the template!-->\n| num_episodes       = 148<!--Only increment as a new episode premieres, per the documentation of the template!-->\n| list_episodes      = List of Chicago P.D. episodes\n| executive_producer = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Dick Wolf]]\n* [[Matt Olmstead]]\n* Danielle Gelber\n* [[Michael Brandt]]\n* [[Derek Haas]]\n* [[Mark Tinker]]\n* Arthur W. Forney\n* [[Peter Jankowski]]\n* Rick Eid\n* Terry Miller\n}}\n| producer           = {{Plainlist|\n* Terry Miller\n* Jamie Pachino\n* Jeremy Beim\n* Michele Greco\n* Maisha Closson\n* Kim Rome\n}}\n| camera             = [[Single-camera setup|